{"tid":1577789,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"思想上的武裝 - 哲學有偈傾 大家都應該睇睇","createTime":"2019-09-18T01:10:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T14:34:41.000Z","uid":32063,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d050a62cfe330bec23610909151f91a959bc8785","tid":1577789,"uid":32063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T01:10:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/w5npso82pKs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fw5npso82pKs&d=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5GDcYOQIx6XO0JIcXsozN2c%3D&h=34abe107\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/w5npso82pKs</a><br />\n<br />\n其實一直有睇依個節目<br />\n咁今次去到一個好切身既題目，<br />\n本人覺得重點有幾個：<br />\n1.和理非與勇武既關係及演化<br />\n2.攬炒概念<br />\n3.勇武既底線，如：是否禍必及妻兒？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁我覺得好重要一個點就係 <br />\n禍及妻兒 係可以 但我哋唔可以話用過份既武力。就算一場戰爭都有分戰爭人員同非戰爭人員<br />\n姐係見到警察仔女就女姦男殺，依種係不合理武力，當然只係依一刻暫時情況係咁。<br />\n<br />\n咁詳細都唔講咁多，最重要希望大家睇完可以有所思考。整理思想可以使人更理解自己應該點做，各位加油。"},{"pid":"8b8587ef8a5ecab3d9e2f335b3c003513e2bc79a","tid":1577789,"uid":32063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T01:44:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee13655b30ac5ef94d703524c6ba67029ad51020","tid":1577789,"uid":65530,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T01:47:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"71714614c1c0fb0da2ff89edd5fb3de592823eb1","tid":1577789,"uid":32063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee13655b30ac5ef94d703524c6ba67029ad51020","tid":1577789,"uid":65530,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T01:47:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:59:54.000Z","msg":"當推廣"},{"pid":"40387cf7e63e7a24af5a16f65ef3613aea4ae81f","tid":1577789,"uid":223765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:06:45.000Z","msg":"喱個高質<br />\n未睇都推咗先"},{"pid":"1c0dc6513309481dda29adeb65ceb0d4b5bfc9fd","tid":1577789,"uid":306925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:08:54.000Z","msg":"借貴寶地<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1577137/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1577137/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n1）警察<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">衰野太多，好難一張文宣講晒</span></span></strong><br />\n2）我地前線手足都開始<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反擊得勁D，反擊畫面</span></span></strong>又會被現在好落力打國際戰的<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府拎黎大造文章，條片正好俾外國能更好地體諒我地</span></span></strong><br />\n3）更好利用一些<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">震撼畫面或者橋段，收籠外國人心</span></strong></span><br />\n4）微電影，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">睇故仔，好多人都會幾OK，有助spread</span></span></strong>我地情況出去<br />\n5）以後我地本地同外國<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣都塞條片的link入去</span></strong></span>，又或者YouTube channel<br />\n<br />\n但廢J我完全不識點樣整呢D片出來，卡通又好真人又好，都唔識，眾籌也沒experience。所以<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">想集結神力，有邊位兄弟覺得有得諗，就幫手spread出去同用力push，小弟廢J P牌仔自push都做唔到</span></span></strong>，sosaad。"},{"pid":"e56c74a1de37772278790dfb64f6a638f5db74f9","tid":1577789,"uid":51467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:31:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3dfcca66adf475464982d5b4f52525da339207d2","tid":1577789,"uid":32063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:44:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f583b3dbad5d7ab6458d27182d0b7d3dafc8433","tid":1577789,"uid":71140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:51:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8266eead559e21ad7f374361f666c9d4f5300155","tid":1577789,"uid":32063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f583b3dbad5d7ab6458d27182d0b7d3dafc8433","tid":1577789,"uid":71140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c